<% new_table = NewTable.new(query) %>

<% if new_table.is_column_order_optimized? %>
  PERFECT!
<% else %>
  Please use the following column order:

  | Column name | Data Type |
  | -------- | ---------------- |
  <% new_table.optimize_column_order.each do |column| %>
  | <%= column[0] %> | <%= column[1] %> |
  <% end %>
<% end %>

For more details check:
https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/development/database/ordering_table_columns.html#ordering-table-columns-in-postgresql
